@{b}About@{ub}
=====

Mnemosyne is an open source disk utility application for AmigaOS 3.2,
which can be used to manage your files and your disk space.

It is coded in C and uses the NDK 3.2. and ReAction.
     
"Mnemosyne", in Greek mythology is the goddess of memory.
     
Mnemosyne is a free software, released under the GNU General Public
License (GPL). You can find the source code of Mnemosyne on GitHub:

Thank you so much for using Mnemosyne!

